## Performance Characteristics

### Meta-Cognition
- **Evaluation Frequency**: On each reflection cycle
- **Memory Usage**: O(n) where n = number of meta-thoughts
- **Time Complexity**: O(m) where m = number of conditions to evaluate

### Contextual Awareness
- **Filtering Overhead**: O(1) per thought
- **Context Switching**: O(1) operation
- **Priority Adjustment**: O(t) where t = number of preferred tags

### Temporal Scheduling
- **Scheduler Tick**: O(s) where s = number of scheduled tasks
- **Time Simulation**: O(t) where t = number of ticks
- **Task Execution**: O(1) per task

